thing.title: Rook 1
thing.author: jmne
thing.description: A very primitive 2.5" chess rook, the first in a series of fabricatable chess pieces.The .skp file is the original design, made in SketchUp.The .stl file was generated directly from SketchUp using the DXF/STL Export plugin.The .gcode file was generated from the .stl file using Skeinforge.This is my very first 3D model. You can probably do better. ;-)
